OL,7,FPeople in Herne Bay say the
OL,8,Fintroduction of red markings on
OL,9,Fresidential streets is a waste of
OL,10,Fmoney.
OL,12,FPainted squares have appeared to alert
OL,13,Fdrivers they're entering a 20mph zone.
OL,15,F#14,000 has been spent on the entrance
OL,16,Fboundaries which Kent County Council
OL,17,Fsays will bring down accidents.
