OL,7,FResident Gavin Woodward said: "Drivers
OL,8,Fare looking ahead not at the floor so
OL,9,Fis it really that worth it? No."
OL,11,FResident Clive Packham said: "I think
OL,12,Fthis will be less safe because people
OL,13,Fhave no idea if we're in 20 or 30. I'm
OL,14,Fafraid to say Herne Bay is an old
OL,15,Fpeople's town. You're looking at
OL,16,Fpeople 60 or above who are still
OL,17,Fdriving and they are confused. They
OL,18,Fhave no idea what's going on. It's
OL,19,Fpandemonium."
