OL,7,FNine road junctions where 30 turns to
OL,8,F20 have been painted in an area where
OL,9,Fthere has been 66 road accidents in
OL,10,Ffive years.
OL,12,FA Kent County Council (KCC)
OL,13,Fspokesperson said: "Nine red entrance
OL,14,Fpatches have been installed in Herne
OL,15,FBay to support the 20mph zone and the
OL,16,F'20' paint will be added when the
OL,17,Fweather allows.
