OL,7,F"The markings provide a clear
OL,8,Findication to drivers that they are
OL,9,Fentering the new speed restriction
OL,10,Farea. The colour is considered most
OL,11,Fappropriate to provide a contrast,
OL,12,Ftherefore highlighting the boundary
OL,13,Fand encouraging self-enforcement. The
OL,14,Fcolour will fade in time.
OL,16,F"The total cost of the entrance
OL,17,Fboundaries is in the region of #14,000
OL,18,Fand was paid for through government
OL,19,Ffunding provided as part of KCC's
OL,20,FActive Travel scheme bid."
