OL,7,FThe markings come as the authority
OL,8,Ffaces criticism about pedestrianising
OL,9,Fpart of the seafront in a bid to
OL,10,Fimprove the economy.
OL,12,FBoth schemes are being funded by the
OL,13,Fgovernment.
OL,15,FLucy Straker from Brake said: "If
OL,16,Fyou're hit as a pedestrian by a car
OL,17,Ftravelling at 30 you're five times
OL,18,Fmore likely to die than you are if
OL,19,Fyou're hit by a car travelling at 20.
